title: Playboy Playmates of the Month 1953-1999 (individually zipped)
description:
Playboy Playmates of the Month 1953-1999 (individually zipped)

Full pictorials from the US edition of Playboy's Playmate of the Month series, from December 1953 (Marilyn Monroe, the very first) to December 1999 (Brooke Richards). There are an average of 30 pictures per folder! Centerfolds are high-res (ca. 2000x3000px) but other pictures are in the 800x600px range, though still very enjoyable.

Every month in every year is represented, but note:
- There were two Playmates in October 1958, Mara Corday and Pat Sheehan. There are two separate folders for that month.
- Playboy was not published in March 1955, so there are no pictures for that month.
- Margaret Scott (aka Marilyn Waltz) was Playmate in February 1954, April 1954, and April 1955. Her pictures all appear under the April 1955 folder, as I don't know which belongs to which.
- Margie Harrison was Playmate in January 1954 and June 1954. Her pictures all appear under the January 1954 folder, as I don't know which belongs to which.
- Janet Pilgrim was Playmate in July 1955, December 1955, and October 1956. The pictures are all under the July 1955 folder, as I don't know which belongs to which.

Please seed!
